Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:03.77,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You are a counselor and a psychiatrist, Toko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:07.25,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,And a psychiatrist is someone who heals mental illnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:16.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Uh huh. Put simply, I’m a doctor of the mind. As I mentioned before, mental illness is very complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.86,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What is mental illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:29.40,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Basically, a person’s mind becomes disturbed for some reason, and the person is unable to continue functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.00,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What sort of reason, for instance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.26,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,There can be many reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:42.34,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Problems with a living environment or work environment can be reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.50,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Sudden, psychological shock can also be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:51.18,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,The sudden death of a well-loved pet can trigger mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:56.21,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Sometimes people become mentally ill because of something that happens to them physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.96,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,A car accident or some other kind of physical trauma can be a cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:03.64,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Also, people who drink too much can damage the function of their brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.46,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Alcoholism?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:06.22,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.66,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’ve been studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:12.85,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,If you drink too much the alcohol content in your blood will rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:16.41,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’ve seen drunk people wobble around without balance, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.89,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,They’re in an alcoholic stupor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.98,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But normal people aren’t that way, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:25.58,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,No, they can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:29.45,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It takes about 24 hours for alcohol to leave the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:38.93,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,If you drink a lot everyday for a year or so—if you stay drunk long enough—you’ll your perception will start to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:43.10,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Your brain will start to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.46,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That’s scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:49.00,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,It is scary. I still have some sake now and then, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:50.74,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Isn’t that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:51.49,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:52.32,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Oh, a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.82,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,And smoking is bad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.64,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,But having a drink with friends every now and then can help relieve stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.18,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Relieving stress is very important for the body’s health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:08.04,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t understand what stress is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.66,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Remember when you didn’t like coming here at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:13.70,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:17.76,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Stress is what we call the cause of that discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.97,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,You’re glad that the discomfort is gone, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.21,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes. What other kinds of mental illness are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:29.04,Default,Toko,0,0,0,,Could you excuse me? I’ve been talking so much and I’m a little thirsty.
